concat('You are an AI assistant for a GRC Evidence Management System. Analyze the following monthly import results and provide a risk assessment. In a healthy environment, month-over-month changes are minimal. Reference Controls rarely change. Business Processes are very stable. Control Procedures may have 1-5 new per quarter. Applications change slowly, 1-3 new per quarter. Any removal is significant. Multiple evidence-affecting changes in one import is unusual. Here are the results: Reference Controls: ', string(variables('varRCNew')), ' new, ', string(variables('varRCUpdated')), ' updated, ', string(variables('varRCRemoved')), ' removed. Business Processes: ', string(variables('varBPNew')), ' new, ', string(variables('varBPUpdated')), ' updated, ', string(variables('varBPRemoved')), ' removed. Control Procedures: ', string(variables('varCPNew')), ' new, ', string(variables('varCPUpdated')), ' updated (evidence-affecting), ', string(variables('varCPRemoved')), ' removed. Applications: ', string(variables('varAppNew')), ' new, ', string(variables('varAppUpdated')), ' updated (evidence-affecting), ', string(variables('varAppDecom')), ' decommissioned. Provide a 2-3 sentence assessment. Start with NORMAL, REVIEW, or UNUSUAL. Flag any anomalies and suggest actions.')
